To build the real firmware:
1. Open the esp32-firmware project in VS Code with ESP-IDF extension
2. Set the device type in sdkconfig: CONFIG_YKP_DEVICE_TYPE_GATEWAY=y
3. Run: idf.py build
4. Find the binary at: build/ykp_gateway.bin
5. Copy it here and rename to ykp_gateway_v1.2.0.bin
